{"tid":604093,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"外語舊歌手分享：80年代沙聲歌后 - Bonnie Tyler","createTime":"2018-03-24T11:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T14:02:12.000Z","uid":40662,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b122b0355da62373a26126125739cceb718fd59e","tid":604093,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T11:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-hv7wKe6n-EQ/WrBYrPL8K4I/AAAAAAAATaU/6Oc6gltIj3sl2fSzRVxHPZ4ct3OvoI1zACLcBGAs/s1600/51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-hv7wKe6n-EQ%2FWrBYrPL8K4I%2FAAAAAAAATaU%2F6Oc6gltIj3sl2fSzRVxHPZ4ct3OvoI1zACLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2F51.jpg&h=bbfa7e98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要數本人最喜愛嘅十大外語女歌手，相信來自英國威爾斯嘅老牌搖滾女唱將Bonnie Tyler定必榜上有名！當年一張風靡全港嘅《The Power Of Love》精選專輯，令我認識到好多首百聽不厭嘅英文老歌，而其中Bonnie Tyler呢一首〈Total Eclipse Of The Heart〉就更加係深深震撼我嘅心靈！佢嗰把沙啞得嚟又鬼咁狂野嘅聲音，充分將歌入面嗰一份失落嘅痛苦心情表露無遺，呢種聲嘶力竭嘅演繹方式，徹底打破我一直以來對靚聲歌手嘅定義同執著。👂🏻<br />\n<br />\n完整全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://timeischanging2013.blogspot.hk/2018/03/CoCoAndMe-March.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimeischanging2013.blogspot.hk%2F2018%2F03%2FCoCoAndMe-March.html&d=4P%2FVYxtlXed%2B3naUXCYKwWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=30ae8fe5\" target=\"_blank\">http://timeischanging2013.blogspot.hk/2018/03/CoCoAndMe-March.html</a>"},{"pid":"96edd301b2d871d507d6296d750c7934e31bb3e5","tid":604093,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T11:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b53a4c8d573b12fce2e30fffaa195fcf5a578a0","tid":604093,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T12:08:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lcOxhH8N3Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlcOxhH8N3Bo&d=4P%2FVYxtlXed%2B3naUXCYKwWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=97e0ed3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lcOxhH8N3Bo